32-25 30th Street, east side, just south of Broadway, showing the rear of the Sanford Mansion, which was purchased by John E. Lockwood in 1864. The vantage point is 31st Street. View 1:  Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  May, 1923
View 2:  P. L Sperr  June 3, 1927
